[src:functional-equations/riemann-zeta-function] One can analytically continue these functions to the *n*-dimensional complex space.
[src:functional-equations/riemann-zeta-function] The special values taken by these functions at positive integer arguments are called multiple zeta values by number theorists and have been connected to many different branches in mathematics and physics.
